        "sentence": "Strengthened cyber security and more knowledge Public sector cyber security levels must be raised and government institutions and business must have access to threat assessments and to advanced knowledge about how to reduce vulnerabilities."
    }, 
    {
        "sentence_id,": "225e8a0692", 
        "tag": [
            {
                "category": "legal measures", 
