            }, 
            {
                "category": "organization measures", 
                "subcategory": [
                    "structure"
                ]
            }
        ], 
        "sentence": "Robust infrastructure in the energy and telecommunications sectors There must be a high level of cyber and information security within the energy and telecommunications sectors."
    }, 
    {
        "sentence_id,": "6760d003e4", 
        "tag": [
            {
                "category": "legal measures", 
                "subcategory": [
                    "secure"
                ]
            }
        ], 
        "sentence": "Denmark as a strong international partner Danish authorities must work with international partners to strengthen cyber and information security through active participation in relevant forums."
    }, 
    {
        "sentence_id,": "0bd794b80b", 
        "tag": [
            {
                "category": "legal measures", 
                "subcategory": [
                    "secure"
                ]
            }
        ], 
        "sentence": "Strong investigation and high level of information Cyber-crime investigations must be strong and competent, and citizens and businesses must be given a better basis for adequately assuming responsibility for security in relation to their own equipment and online conduct."
    }, 
    {
        "sentence_id,": "a2df2f8a30", 
        "tag": [
            {
                "category": "legal measures", 
                "subcategory": [
                    "secure"
                ]
            }, 
            {
                "category": "capacity building", 
                "subcategory": [
                    "enhance"
                ]
            }
        ], 
        "sentence": "The initiatives aim to ensure the maintaining of adequate security levels and will serve to significantly enhance Danish cyber and information security efforts."
    }, 
    {
        "sentence_id,": "dd76c24209", 
        "tag": [
            {
                "category": "legal measures", 
                "subcategory": [
                    "secure", 
                    "protection"
                ]
            }
        ], 
        "sentence": "It is however important to stress that complete protection against breakdowns, compromise and other security incidents is unattainable."
    }, 
    {
        "sentence_id,": "9645a36347", 
        "tag": [
            {
                "category": "legal measures", 
                "subcategory": [
                    "secure"
                ]
            }
        ], 
        "sentence": "Cyber and information security threats are ever-changing and efforts to ensure a high level of security must be continuously improved and renewed."
    }, 
    {
        "sentence_id,": "f0af5df85e", 
        "tag": [
            {
                "category": "legal measures", 
                "subcategory": [
