            {
                "category": "organization measures", 
                "subcategory": [
                    "structure"
                ]
            }
        ], 
        "sentence": "Professionalizing the governments cyber and information security effort is essential to the protection of digital infrastructures which important functions in society rely upon."
    }, 
    {
        "sentence_id,": "a511bff017", 
        "tag": [
            {
