            {
                "category": "organization measures", 
                "subcategory": [
                    "structure", 
                    "strategy"
                ]
            }
        ], 
        "sentence": "The strategy is furthermore focused on cyber and information security within the energy and telecommunications sectors where private companies own and support a large part of the infrastructure."
    }, 
    {
        "sentence_id,": "5fda733831", 
        "tag": [
